{"tid":480184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瘋狂電單車逆線飆5公里","createTime":"2017-11-26T01:13:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T04:53:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"043f8f2d9e5397367bb2cb270c638671abdd1562","tid":480184,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T01:13:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171126/20226091\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171126%2F20226091&d=3WmJyH6EkxGsGwayycMgSAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=181b3bd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171126%2F20226091&h=782d9371\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171126/20226091</a><br />\n<br />\n瘋狂電單車逆線飆5公里<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名因為危險駕駛及撞死人三度入獄男子，昨凌晨駕駛一輛偷來的電單車在葵涌風馳電掣，其間遇上方警方隱形戰車截查，逃避追捕時逆線及衝燈狂飆5.3公里，其後誤闖勵敬懲教所，最終人車翻側，失手就擒，警方以6宗罪拘捕該名司機，先將他帶往醫院接受治療，再帶署扣查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171126/large/26la4p06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171126%2Flarge%2F26la4p06.jpg&h=7675dc48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方事後拖走電單車。黎志偉攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被捕司機曾撞死人判囚<br />\n<br />\n被捕的姓黃男子，38歲，涉嫌擅自取去交通工具、超速駕駛、危險駕駛、駕駛時沒有第三者保險、無牌駕駛和駕駛未領牌車輛被捕。據了解，黃自2000年起干犯超過10次交通條款，在2004及2006年，他分別因危險駕駛入獄3個月及4個月，其後更被法庭判停牌至2010年。2007年10月，他在停牌期間駕駛私家車於柴灣大潭道落斜，駛至柴灣道交界時撞倒一輛電單車，引致26歲電單車女乘客傷重不治，被判入獄一年10個月及停牌至2015年。<br />\n<br />\n昨凌晨2時許，警方新界南交通部隱形戰車在葵涌道巡邏時，發現一輛Kawasaki 600cc電單車高速行駛，警員遂示意停車接受檢查，但鐵騎士卻加速開行，隱形戰車啣尾窮追，電單車沿葵涌道往大窩口逃走，其後轉入健全街，逆線右轉出青山公路，隱形戰車亮燈尾隨追趕，鐵騎士疑慌不擇路，其後駛進華泰路倔頭路，在走投無路之下，他趁閘欄未有落下，竟衝進勵敬懲教所，未幾在一處斜路失事翻側，司機倒地受傷，被捕後送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n■記者潘志能"},{"pid":"cd1ef61a3592439fd9996537439ece9eff20e984","tid":480184,"uid":86545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T01:15:05.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"dcc47874dfe64b054d47831d5171c2e4a087c6ca","tid":480184,"uid":68375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T01:23:42.000Z","msg":"槍斃啦"},{"pid":"8281de253a99e3b9f526ee2818208bc399095f48","tid":480184,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T01:39:49.000Z","msg":"偷車慣手<br />\n<br />\n搵食姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847b853ef1b84252de818741d59365bea71bb5ae","tid":480184,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T01:41:21.000Z","msg":"佢坐監個陣諗緊乜"},{"pid":"86a83e37a77a8a7b9481ad8e236b080e37ed5666","tid":480184,"uid":71257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T03:36:53.000Z","msg":"希望佢死全家"},{"pid":"87b0e839f0d848a2a42ddd6c113aa16ed2e29b6c","tid":480184,"uid":25866,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T04:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 600都走唔甩<br />\n衰唔識路上高速<br />\n你上200都冇人敢跟、當冇跟過算"},{"pid":"621f9f4db5dddd439aae8e8ff1229584befa4f96","tid":480184,"uid":25866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T04:53:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hhmaOCEdxOk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhhmaOCEdxOk&d=3WmJyH6EkxGsGwayycMgSAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=15f1713a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hhmaOCEdxOk</a>"}]}